{"tid":1294772,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"《Uncharted》電影導演確認將不會直接採用遊戲劇情","createTime":"2019-07-08T00:08:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T03:07:03.000Z","uid":75050,"like":7,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"606019b2fa37c9d30002e76bb9adaca90212c918","tid":1294772,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T00:08:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/NowzPlay/posts/2374111356192705\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FNowzPlay%2Fposts%2F2374111356192705&d=Tc8prIKBo9hF1z3tnQ%2BJRiHJFIlRN37b%2BuZTNWj4Tkw%3D&h=b926dcff\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/NowzPlay/posts/2374111356192705</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RK6rxYc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRK6rxYc.jpg&h=f1ce782f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>【業界】《Uncharted》電影導演確認將不會直接採用遊戲劇情</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n  《Uncharted》電影目前已經定檔2020年12月18日上映，不過關於該片的具體細節始終嚴格保密。比如大家最關心的一個問題就是，電影中Nathan Drake究竟會踏上怎樣的冒險。因為演員Tom Holland扮演的是年輕時期的Drake，所以劇情方面可能有很大發揮空間。<br />\n<br />\n  最近，在接受媒體採訪時，該片導演Dan Trachtenberg透露了一些消息，看起來，《Uncharted》電影的劇情將不會套用遊戲劇情，因為那樣的遊戲改編電影只能提供二流體驗。<br />\n<br />\n  在採訪中，Trachtenberg特別提到了他想要避免走上老路。<strong><ins> &ldquo;我曾經收到過這個故事的不同版本，但沒有任何版本讓我感到有趣，因為我並不想走遊戲已經走過的路。&rdquo;</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n  他繼續講解道，複製與粘貼出來的作品永遠都不可能超越遊戲原本的體驗。 <strong><ins>&ldquo;我覺得在拍攝遊戲改編電影的時候，照搬遊戲劇情是毫無價值的。如果我們單純地複制遊戲內容，那麼只能提供二流體驗，不可能超過他們在遊戲中已經獲得過的難忘體驗。&rdquo;</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n  Trachtenberg對他和創意團隊目前編寫出來的劇情表現出很強的自信。 &ldquo;如果Naughty Dog想要再以Drake和Sullivan為主角再次製作一部《Uncharted》的話，那麼電影的劇情很可能會提供很好的參考和借鑒。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n  目前《Uncharted》電影尚未公佈劇照、海報或宣傳片，<strong><ins>事實上，本片的選角甚至可能還沒有完成。直到今年3月份，Sony依然在尋找Sullivan的合適扮演者。</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n  如果一切進展順利，《Uncharted》電影將於2020年12月18日上映。<br />\n<br />\n-----"},{"pid":"814a9c3dbef26770f05ad5df42155e1da8029287","tid":1294772,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T00:59:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf7330b603dc6ada9d2fb768f6be0563bf812dbd","tid":1294772,"uid":49151,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T02:38:35.000Z","msg":"不了"},{"pid":"faee84306d80558d2c20d8b0beef022afd2f4cb5","tid":1294772,"uid":187647,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T05:10:57.000Z","msg":"搵Tom Holland做Drake無哂佬味"},{"pid":"664cf8cdb56b11d757efdf011595ebce21742c66","tid":1294772,"uid":60412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"faee84306d80558d2c20d8b0beef022afd2f4cb5","tid":1294772,"uid":187647,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T05:10:57.000Z","msg":"搵Tom Holland做Drake無哂佬味"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T05:19:19.000Z","msg":"演佢後生版wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83726ca799971fe99a31dd19d68b49881d1901b0","tid":1294772,"uid":65201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"faee84306d80558d2c20d8b0beef022afd2f4cb5","tid":1294772,"uid":187647,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T05:10:57.000Z","msg":"搵Tom Holland做Drake無哂佬味"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T05:19:37.000Z","msg":"因為演員Tom Holland扮演的是年輕時期的Drake<br />\n<br />\n應該有另一個演員做中年Drake<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01dbccf8b22b422160e2a5f7111a33849f87c503","tid":1294772,"uid":65201,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T05:20:49.000Z","msg":"btw唔照搬遊戲劇情既原因同考量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有d見地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae0b8448672522f5d29e34de46d14536b7f78005","tid":1294772,"uid":48791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T05:48:44.000Z","msg":"爛片預定"},{"pid":"0a3f55f0d7568bf894544e503c6a2618a017dbf4","tid":1294772,"uid":187647,"like":0,"dislike":2,"sco